title: 150: The Ultimate Supermarket Haul Episode (Kroger, Albertsons, Meijer and more!)
itunes:title: The Ultimate Supermarket Haul Episode (Kroger, Albertsons, Meijer and more!)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the crew are trying some super-great finds like omelet rolls, cereal-inspired oatmeal, BBQ sauce with a secret ingredient, a really inventive dairy find, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a breakfast pastry from Kellogg’s that only has 100 calories and is so YUMMY! What are you waiting for? Push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Get ready to update your shopping list! Must-have finds are coming your way in this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
